high_descs: turn right, walk to the counter, turn right, walk to the side of the table
grab the bread on the table
turn right, walk across the room the refrigerator
put the bread in the refrigerator for a while, take it out
turn left, walk to the white table
put the bread on the table
anns.task_desc: cool the bread in the refrigerator, put it on the table

high_descs: Turn right and walk two steps then turn right and walk to the window and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the bread off of the table.
Turn right and walk two steps then turn left and walk to the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the bottom portion of the fridge and place the bread to the right hand side of the top rack and close the door letting it chill before retrieving it and closing the door again.
Turn left and walk until you are by the table then turn right to face it you should be looking at a salt shaker now.
Place the bread on the table to the right of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on the table.

high_descs: Walk around to the left side of the table in front of you.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Turn right and walk forward to the fridge.
Place the bread on the top shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the bread out.
Turn left and walk back to the table on the right.
Place the bread on the table to the right of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the table with the bread and salt on it.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator
Open the door and put the bread on the top shelf
Take the bread out of the refrigerator and put it on the table on the right.
Set the bread on the table by the salt.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a loaf of bread and put it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table near the window.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Walk around the table and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread and pick it up again.
Return to the table by the window.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on the table by the window.

high_descs: Turn right then turn right again and walk toward the window, turn to face the white table.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the bread on the top shelf, wait, and then open the fridge door again and take out the bread.
Turn left and walk back to the white table. Turn right.
Place the bread on the table to the right of the salt shaker.
